fects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/76322/', '', 'Carisoprodol, Chlorzoxazone, Baclofen, Methocarbamol, Chlormezanone', '', 1767369485);
